他大量失血

829
00:42:14,875 --> 00:42:16,775
去别家医院
Go to another hospital.

830
00:42:17,144 --> 00:42:18,372
快开门
Let's go. Open the door.

831
00:42:19,079 --> 00:42:19,841
你认得这些人？
- You now these guys? - Yeah.

832
00:42:19,980 --> 00:42:21,038
认得

833
