你确定？
- You sure? - They're here all the time.

834
00:42:22,282 --> 00:42:23,476
他们常来这里

835
00:42:23,817 --> 00:42:24,681
开门
Open the door.

836
00:42:28,555 --> 00:42:29,419
把你的外套脱掉
- Take your jacket off. - What?

837
00:42:29,556 --> 00:42:30,250
什么？

