They shot me anyway.

849
00:43:19,639 --> 00:43:21,072
老天爷
Jesus Christ.

850
00:43:21,441 --> 00:43:23,739
他得立刻手术，送进外伤病房
He needs surgery now.

851
00:43:23,877 --> 00:43:24,400
好
Can I take him to Trauma one?

852
00:43:24,544 --> 00:43:25,408
好的
- Okay. - All right.

853
