情况如何？
- What do we got? - Gunshot wound to the belly.

854
00:43:27,314 --> 00:43:28,406
腹部枪伤

855
00:43:28,782 --> 00:43:29,840
急救人员有做任何处置吗？
- Did we get anything from the EMTs? - No.

856
00:43:29,983 --> 00:43:30,449
没有
Doc Turner, we'll need a hand. Oh, man.

857
00:43:30,650 --> 00:43:32,140
透纳医生，我们需要你帮忙

858
