我帮不上忙，这是枪伤
No, I can't handle this.

863
00:43:44,498 --> 00:43:46,659
我是心脏外科的，不是急诊科
This is a gut shot. I'm a cardiac surgeon.

864
00:43:46,833 --> 00:43:48,824
这跟骑脚踏车一样简单
I'm not an Emergency Room physician.

865
00:43:46,967 --> 00:43:48,059
It's like riding a bike, doc.

866
00:43:49,002 --> 00:43:50,333
就假装你有收费吧
Pretend you're getting paid.

867
00:43:50,971 --> 00:43:52,905
这是萍果跟橘子的差别，不行
This is apples and oranges, okay?

868
00:43:53,039 --> 00:43:54,370
他快死了，救救他
He's dying. Help me.

869
00:43:54,508 --> 00:43:55,372
我想救他，但我没有K
- I'd like to help him. I haven't done- -

870
00:43:55,509 --> 00:43:56,635
动手吧
- Do it!

871
00:43:59,146 --> 00:44:01,046
注射止痛剂，局部麻醉
Seventy-five milligrams Demerol I. V. Lidocaine, two percent local.

872
00:44:01,181 --> 00:44:02,045
立刻洗手
Scrub right now.

873
00:44:02,182 --> 00:44:03,479
局部麻醉免了，改全身麻醉
Forget the local. I'm putting him to sleep.

874
00:44:04,184 --> 00:44:07,381
我出去后要告这家医院跟保全
When I get out of here,

875
00:44:05,819 --> 00:44:07,616
I'm suing this hospital and your security company.

876
00:44:07,521 --> 00:44:09,751
你凭什么认为你一定能出去？
What makes you so sure you're getting out of here?

877
00:44:22,769 --> 00:44:23,793
来了
Here we go.

878
00:44:38,418 --> 00:44:39,851
好了，请站到线后
All right, you got to stand behind the line, sir.

879
00:44:40,320 --> 00:44:44,051
把这辆车弄出去，谢谢
Move this out of here for me? Thank you.

880
00:44:44,691 --> 00:44:47,285
副队长，麻烦大了
Lieutenant. We got a real problem here.

881
00:44:47,394 --> 00:44:47,917
什么麻烦？
- What's that? - This guy's in for the long haul.

882
00:44:48,061 --> 00:44:49,619
这家伙准备长期抗战

883
00:44:49,796 --> 00:44:51,024
他锁住急诊室
He's locked the E. R., barricaded himself in

884
00:44:51,198 --> 00:44:54,258
把自己困在里面，关闭电梯电源

885
00:44:52,866 --> 00:44:54,197
and killed the power in the elevators.

886
00:44:54,434 --> 00:44:57,403
我们若破门而入 他会大开杀戒
If we bust down the door,

887
00:44:55,769 --> 00:44:57,236
this son of a bitch might start killing people.

888
00:44:57,571 --> 00:45:00,005
急诊室里有两架监视摄影机
There's two video cameras hidden in the E. R.

889
00:45:00,140 --> 00:45:01,971
是属于医院监视系统
The hospital's surveillance.

890
00:45:02,108 --> 00:45:03,234
我们正在设法连结视讯
We're setting up a video tap.

891
00:45:03,410 --> 00:45:04,377
你负责保全？
You in charge of security?

892
00:45:04,511 --> 00:45:07,605
不，是皮瓦利，他今天休假
No. That's Wally Pitoniak.

893
00:45:07,747 --> 00:45:10,147
不再是了，叫他过来
It's his day off.

894
00:45:07,947 --> 00:45:09,244
Not anymore, it ain't.

895
00:45:09,382 --> 00:45:10,679
Get him down here.

896
00:45:13,320 --> 00:45:14,446
能弄条安全的通话线路吗？
Can you get me a secure line?

897
00:45:14,621 --> 00:45:14,985
行
Yes.

898
00:45:15,121 --> 00:45:17,248
副队长，里面的人有无线电
Lieutenant, we got one of our guys on the inside.

899
00:45:17,390 --> 00:45:19,654
你也许会想试试
He's got a walkie-talkie.

900
00:45:18,658 --> 00:45:20,091
You might want to try this.

901
00:45:20,327 --> 00:45:22,659
切断急诊室的电话线路
Put a clamp on all pone lines to the E. R.

902
00:45:22,796 --> 00:45:25,264
他若拿起电话，我要他跟我谈
If he picks up the phone, I want him talking to me.

903
00:45:25,398 --> 00:45:26,558
没问题
Done.

904
00:45:27,901 --> 00:45:28,799
谁是这里的负责人？
- Who's in charge here? - Rebecca Payne, sir.

905
00:45:28,935 --> 00:45:30,232
潘芮贝

906
00:45:30,504 --> 00:45:31,801
她今天也休假
It's her day off too.

907
00:45:31,938 --> 00:45:34,634
天，这医院到底有没有人上班
Does anybody work at this hospital?

908
00:45:34,908 --> 00:45:35,932
今天是周六
It's Saturday, sir.

909
00:45:36,076 --> 00:45:37,065
那又怎样？
So what?

910
00:45:37,744 --> 00:45:39,974
周六也会有人生病，不是吗？
People get sick on Saturday, don't they?

911
00:45:46,653 --> 00:45:47,620
没哭了
No cry.

912
00:45:48,488 --> 00:45:49,614
没哭了
No cry.

913
00:45:52,292 --> 00:45:55,159
亚契先生，我要帮她做内诊
Mr. Archibald, I need to do an internal exam on her.

914
00:45:55,395 --> 00:45:56,453
你要带她去哪？
- Where are you going to take here? - Examination room there.

915
00:45:56,696 --> 00:45:57,788
那边的诊疗室

916
00:45:58,031 --> 00:45:59,259
好，去吧
Good. Go.

917
00:46:00,700 --> 00:46:04,136
Oh, my God.

918
00:46:02,736 --> 00:46:03,703
天啊

919
00:46:07,607 --> 00:46:09,370
记住，这不是你的错
Remember, it ain't your fault.

920
00:46:09,509 --> 00:46:10,441
对不起
Excuse me.

921
00:46:11,878 --> 00:46:14,278
我未婚妻的手可能断了
I think my fiancee might have broken her arm.

922
00:46:14,414 --> 00:46:16,609
是不是有人能医治她？
Could somebody take a look at her, please?

923
00:46:16,750 --> 00:46:17,910
当然，怎么回事？
Sure, what happened?

924
00:46:18,718 --> 00:46:19,878
有个醉鬼闯红灯
- A drunk ran a red light- - - He slammed into us.

925
00:46:20,020 --> 00:46:21,487
他撞上我们

926
00:46:21,621 --> 00:46:22,053
对吧？
- Right? - Yep.

927
00:46:22,188 --> 00:46:23,120
对
- It was an accident. - Yes, it was.

928
00:46:23,256 --> 00:46:24,120
那是个意外

929
00:46:24,257 --> 00:46:25,224
没错

930
00:46:27,594 --> 00:46:29,027
这是警察
This is the police department.

931
00:46:29,396 --> 00:46:31,694
我要跟负责的人谈
I'm speaking to the man in charge.

932
00:46:31,865 --> 00:46:33,560
请打开无线电
Please pick up the walkie-talkie.

933
00:46:34,668 --> 00:46:36,260
这栋建筑已被团团围住
The building is surrounded.

934
00:46:36,436 --> 00:46:37,596
你们已无法出入
There's no way in or out,

935
00:46:37,671 --> 00:46:40,299
你若听见，我建议你接听
So if you hear me, I advise you to respond.

936
00:46:41,241 --> 00:46:42,299
喂？
Hello?

937
00:46:43,376 --> 00:46:45,071
喂？有人在吗？
Hello? Is anyone there?

938
00:46:46,513 --> 00:46:47,445
有
Yeah.

939
00:46:48,214 --> 00:46:51,377
我是芝加哥警局的葛副队长
This is Lieutenant Frank Grimes of the Chicago Police Department.

940
00:46:51,751 --> 00:46:53,241
你是负责的人？
Are you the man in charge?

941
00:46:55,889 --> 00:46:56,981
没错
That's right.

942
00:46:57,390 --> 00:46:58,652
请问你是？
Who am I speaking to?

943
00:47:00,927 --> 00:47:01,985
约翰
John...

944
00:47:03,897 --> 00:47:04,989
老Q
...Q.

945
00:47:06,933 --> 00:47:08,833
好，约翰老Q
All right, John Q.

946
00:47:09,769 --> 00:47:11,896
重覆，我是葛副队长
Again, I'm Lieutenant Grimes,

947
00:47:12,038 --> 00:47:13,938
但我要你叫我法兰，可以吗？
But I want you to call me Frank. Can you do that?

948
00:47:14,074 --> 00:47:15,132
好，法兰
Sure, Frank.

949
00:47:15,442 --> 00:47:16,932
我负责人质谈判
I'll be the hostage negotiator.

950
00:47:17,077 --> 00:47:20,069
我当警察35年，我都这么做
I've been a cop for 35 years.

951
00:47:20,380 --> 00:47:22,007
我不玩花样，也不耍人
This is all I do.

952
00:47:20,280 --> 00:47:22,111
I don't play games. I don't fool around.

953
00:47:22,148 --> 00:47:25,242
我说的话，你绝对可以相信
So if I say something, you can take it to the bank.

954
00:47:25,619 --> 00:47:26,745
我们来谈谈吧
Now, let's get down to it.

955
00:47:27,621 --> 00:47:28,883
有人受伤吗？
Is anybody hurt?

956
00:47:29,656 --> 00:47:32,147
这是急诊室，大家都受了伤
It's an E. R. Everybody's hurt.

957
00:47:32,959 --> 00:47:33,983
他们很好
They're fine.

958
00:47:34,260 --> 00:47:34,783
很好
Good. An long as it stays that way, we can keep talking.

959
00:47:34,928 --> 00:47:37,658
继续这样，我们就能好好谈

960
00:47:37,831 --> 00:47:39,560
你想要什么？
What is it that you want?

961
00:47:39,933 --> 00:47:42,026
你找到潘芮贝
You find Rebecca Payne,

962
00:47:42,202 --> 00:47:44,261
希望纪念医院的行政主管
Hope Memorial's administrative supervisor.

963
00:47:44,437 --> 00:47:45,631
找到她
You find her.

964
00:47:45,772 --> 00:47:49,435
叫她把我孩子放上移植名单
You tell her I want my kid's name on the donor's list.

965
00:47:49,643 --> 00:47:52,305
听清楚了？把我孩子放上名单
My kid's name on the donor's list.

966
00:47:52,646 --> 00:47:53,476
是儿子还是女儿？
- Kid boy or girl? - A boy.

967
00:47:53,647 --> 00:47:54,614
儿子
I got two boys myself, John.

968
00:47:54,948 --> 00:47:56,779
我自己有两个儿子

969
00:47:57,651 --> 00:47:59,312
两个女儿、两个儿子
Two girls and two boys.

970
00:48:01,588 --> 00:48:03,078
别想耍我，法兰，你明白吗？
Don't handle me, Frank. You understand me?

971
00:48:03,223 --> 00:48:05,987
我不喜欢被耍，我没那么笨
I don't want to be handled.

972
00:48:04,424 --> 00:48:06,119
It insults my intelligence.

973
00:48:06,126 --> 00:48:09,721
别激动，约翰，千万别激动
Take it easy, John. The idea's not to get too excited.

974
00:48:09,996 --> 00:48:12,089
我想怎样就怎样，你明白吗？
I'm going to take it any way I can get it.

975
00:48:12,265 --> 00:48:13,323
这是我的要求
You understand me?

976
00:48:13,500 --> 00:48:14,524
要是做不到
Now, this is what I want.

977
00:48:14,701 --> 00:48:15,793
你就会害死人
If I don't get it...

978
00:48:15,969 --> 00:48:17,596
听明白了？
...there'll be some dead bodies on your hands.

979
00:48:17,737 --> 00:48:21,935
我听的很清楚，我会写下来
Understand me?

980
00:48:17,837 --> 00:48:19,964
I hear you loud and clear.

981
00:48:20,273 --> 00:48:22,207
I'll jot that down. Rebecca Payne. Right?

982
00:48:22,075 --> 00:48:22,905
潘芮贝，对吧？
All right.

983
00:48:23,043 --> 00:48:23,702
对

984
00:48:24,878 --> 00:48:26,971
外面有很多警察，约翰
Now, there're a lot of cops out here, John.

985
00:48:28,615 --> 00:48:30,378
你确定你要这么做？
Sure you want to go through with this?

986
00:48:30,517 --> 00:48:31,745
对，我确定
Yeah, I'm sure.

987
00:48:33,420 --> 00:48:34,819
好，等着吧
All right, sit tight.

988
00:48:35,055 --> 00:48:37,387
你的处境很艰困，有很多问题
You're in a tough spot, John.

989
00:48:37,524 --> 00:48:39,287
但你若跟我合作，讲理一点
A lot of trouble.

990
00:48:37,457 --> 00:48:38,389
But if you work with me,

991
00:48:39,426 --> 00:48:41,291
我们总会想出解决的办法
if you're reasonable, we'll figure a way out.

992
00:48:41,428 --> 00:48:44,124
我们必须对彼此有坚定信念
We have to have faith in one another.

993
00:48:44,431 --> 00:48:45,125
为什么？
Why is that, Frank?

994
00:48:45,298 --> 00:48:46,390
为什么？
Why?

995
00:48:47,467 --> 00:48:49,435
信念就是这样
That's what faith's all about.

996
00:48:49,703 --> 00:48:52,137
去相信你不想相信的东西
Believing what you don't want to believe.

997
