I'm not kidding around, Frank.

1253
00:59:34,880 --> 00:59:35,847
表现诚意，约翰
- Good faith, John. - Good faith only takes you so far.

1254
00:59:35,981 --> 00:59:37,573
诚意到此为止

1255
00:59:37,717 --> 00:59:40,618
