We have to move her to Maternity immediately.

1261
00:59:50,696 --> 00:59:51,560
约翰
- John. - Hang on, Frank.

1262
00:59:51,664 --> 00:59:52,596
等等，法兰
Right down here.

1263
00:59:52,798 --> 00:59:53,560
在这里

1264
00:59:55,468 --> 00:59:56,799
怎么回事？
- What the hell is going on? - Do you know this man?

1265
00:59:56,936 --> 00:59:57,960
认得这个人吗？

1266
01:00:01,273 --> 01:00:04,003
约翰亚契，他儿子在加护病房
His name is John Archibald.

1267
01:00:04,143 --> 01:00:07,112
派人去病房，我要跟母亲谈
He has a son in ICU.

1268
01:00:04,109 --> 01:00:05,041
Put people on the door.

1269
01:00:05,177 --> 01:00:07,145
I need to talk to the mother.

1270
01:00:07,246 --> 01:00:08,076
你在吗，法兰？
Are you there, Frank.

1271
01:00:08,214 --> 01:00:09,806
我在，约翰
I'm here, John. I'm here.

1272
01:00:09,949 --> 01:00:11,075
我改变主意了
I changed my mind.

1273
01:00:12,451 --> 01:00:13,941
我要放一些人质
I'll let some of the hostages go.

1274
01:00:14,086 --> 01:00:15,553
很好，约翰，这样做很对
That's great, John.

1275
01:00:15,688 --> 01:00:17,679
但等我一开始放人
But when I do, the clock starts. You understand?

1276
01:00:17,823 --> 01:00:19,586
就开始计时了，明白吗？

1277
01:00:19,992 --> 01:00:21,619
现在4点15
It's 4:15.

1278
01:00:21,961 --> 01:00:24,953
你有一小时，到5点15，懂吗
You got one hour.

1279
01:00:23,095 --> 01:00:25,188
You got till 5:15. Understand, Frank.

1280
01:00:25,097 --> 01:00:27,565
要是我儿子到时没登上名单
If my boy's not on that list by 5:15, somebody is going to die.

1281
01:00:27,733 --> 01:00:29,030
就有人会丧命

1282
01:00:29,168 --> 01:00:30,135
约翰，别做傻事
- Don't be stupid. - 5:15, Frank!

1283
01:00:30,269 --> 01:00:31,293
5点15，法兰
Five-one-five, something happens for me!

1284
01:00:31,470 --> 01:00:35,031
5点15分，快去设法

1285
01:00:35,174 --> 01:00:35,902
我明白了
Got it.

1286
01:00:36,041 --> 01:00:37,508
你是警察，快找验尸官吧
You're a cop. Call the coroner.

1287
01:00:39,678 --> 01:00:41,270
这太糟了，法兰
This is bad, Frank.

1288
01:00:41,747 --> 01:00:43,908
这一定要赶快解决
This has just got to go away.

1289
01:00:46,786 --> 01:00:49,186
好了，蜜丽
All right, Miriam.

1290
01:00:49,455 --> 01:00:50,979
放轻松，不会有事的
Relax, everything's going to be okay. Our baby will be fine.

1291
01:00:51,123 --> 01:00:52,283
我们的宝贝会很好的，别担心
- And Rosa. - Yes?

1292
01:00:52,425 --> 01:00:52,823
还有萝莎

1293
01:00:52,958 --> 01:00:53,356
什么？
Let's go.

1294
01:00:53,492 --> 01:00:54,220
走吧

1295
01:00:54,360 --> 01:00:56,260
亚契先生
Mr. Archibald?

1296
01:00:57,396 --> 01:00:58,886
请让我先生一起走
Please let my husband come with me.

1297
01:00:59,064 --> 01:01:01,726
不，你先出去，我不会有事的
Baby, no, I need you to get out of here.

1298
01:01:01,901 --> 01:01:04,734
我走好了，我无牵无挂
I'll be okay.

1299
01:01:01,767 --> 01:01:04,759
Shit, I'll go. I'm free.

1300
01:01:04,870 --> 01:01:05,359
史提，不要
Steve, no.

1301
01:01:05,538 --> 01:01:06,596
你算不算男人啊？
- What kind of man are you? - Screw you, Tyrone.

1302
01:01:06,772 --> 01:01:08,239
去你的，黑金刚

1303
01:01:08,374 --> 01:01:10,899
什么？去我的？黑金刚？
What? Screw me, Tyrone?

1304
01:01:11,043 --> 01:01:12,010
去我的？
Screw me?!

1305
01:01:12,144 --> 01:01:13,634
等等，别激动
Wait a minute, all right? Just relax- -

1306
01:01:18,784 --> 01:01:20,342
干的好，大老粗
That's right, tough guy.

1307
01:01:26,459 --> 01:01:28,017
茱莉，宝贝，快拿枪
Julie, baby, get the gun!

1308
01:01:29,895 --> 01:01:31,055
快捡起枪
Rick up that gun!

1309
01:01:31,430 --> 01:01:33,955
快射他，朝他的脸开枪
Now, shoot him! Shoot him right in the face, Julie!

1310
01:01:34,266 --> 01:01:36,530
朝他的脸开枪，快拿枪
Shoot him right in the face! Get the gun!

1311
01:01:36,669 --> 01:01:38,296
拿枪啊
Get the gun.

1312
01:01:39,472 --> 01:01:41,497
干嘛，你疯了？
What, are you crazy?!

1313
01:01:41,674 --> 01:01:43,266
