别瞎操心
Don't worry about anything.

1338
01:03:06,258 --> 01:03:08,453
我会永远在你身边
I'll always be there for you.

1339
01:03:11,497 --> 01:03:12,464
别开枪
Don't shoot!

1340
01:03:17,336 --> 01:03:20,430
我要释放人质，别开枪
I'm letting some hostages go! Don't shoot!

1341
01:03:22,107 --> 01:03:23,768
好，你们俩个
All right, you two.

1342
01:03:24,710 --> 01:03:26,610
走吧，你们俩个
Let's go, both of you.

1343
01:03:26,979 --> 01:03:29,277
谢谢你、谢谢你
Thank you. Thank you.

1344
01:03:31,417 --> 01:03:33,612
好了，萝莎，你也是
All right, all right. Rose, you too.

1345
01:03:34,920 --> 01:03:36,615
好，好好照顾小孩
All right, Take care of the baby.

1346
01:03:36,755 --> 01:03:39,315
