...who will be debriefed by the crisis team.

1348
01:03:43,162 --> 01:03:46,620
约翰老Q能帮小孩弄到心脏吗？
Will John Q. Get a heart for his little boy?

1349
01:03:46,699 --> 01:03:50,226
