Only time will tell.

1350
01:03:48,300 --> 01:03:49,927
From Hope Memorial Hospital...

1351
01:03:50,402 --> 01:03:52,632
持枪暴徒掌控急诊室之后
Is it true a gunshot victim was dropped off.

1352
01:03:52,705 --> 01:03:55,139
是否真有枪伤病患被送进去？
After the gunman took over the E. R?

1353
01:03:55,274 --> 01:03:57,469
