Ma'am, do you have any comments about the gunman?

1360
01:04:10,122 --> 01:04:12,249
约翰老Q，很好的人
John Q., very good man.

1361
01:04:12,391 --> 01:04:13,358
持枪暴徒？
- The gunman? - Very good man.

1362
01:04:13,492 --> 01:04:15,460
很好的人

1363
01:04:25,537 --> 01:04:26,333
里面有摄影机
They got a camera in there.

1364
01:04:26,472 --> 01:04:28,167
