1379
01:04:59,371 --> 01:05:00,531
没有医疗保险
If you'd like to change it, you should call your congressman.

1380
01:05:00,673 --> 01:05:02,004
想改变这情况，去找国会议员
Excuse me.

1381
01:05:02,141 --> 01:05:02,971
抱歉

1382
01:05:03,642 --> 01:05:06,167
何不告诉他，他儿子在名单上
Why don't we just tell him his son's name's on the list?

1383
01:05:06,311 --> 01:05:07,801
那不是很好吗？
I mean, doesn't that make sense?

1384
01:05:09,014 --> 01:05:10,606
他反正也不会知道真相
How's he going to know, anyway?

1385
01:05:13,052 --> 01:05:16,488
长官，抱歉，请你过来看看
Sir? Pardon me, can you come take a look at this?

1386
01:05:20,659 --> 01:05:22,923
这是皮华利，保安主管
Sarge, Chief, this is Wally Pitoniak, head of security.

1387
01:05:23,062 --> 01:05:23,551
你好
- How are you? - Nice to meet you.

1388
01:05:23,696 --> 01:05:24,287
幸会
I got your spot.

1389
01:05:24,463 --> 01:05:25,930
我帮你找到狙击点

1390
01:05:26,465 --> 01:05:27,625
你们在这里
Here's your site.

1391
01:05:28,400 --> 01:05:31,631
那里就是最好的点
That's going to be your perch.

1392
01:05:32,104 --> 01:05:33,230
X代表你的电话
The X is your phone.

1393
01:05:34,406 --> 01:05:35,236
哪只电话？
- Which phone? - Bring it up, Jeff.

1394
01:05:35,374 --> 01:05:36,306
靠近一点

1395
01:05:39,745 --> 01:05:41,337
那里那只电话
That phone right there.

1396
01:05:44,249 --> 01:05:45,079
是的，汤姆
It is, Tom.

1397
01:05:45,217 --> 01:05:48,084
孟局长仍说会采取必要行动
But Chief Monroe maintains that police will do what's necessary.

1398
01:05:48,220 --> 01:05:51,712
以确保人质的生命与安全
...to preserve the lives and safety of these hostages.

1399
01:05:52,124 --> 01:05:53,113
这个国家
This country, man.

1400
01:05:53,258 --> 01:05:55,021
不管去到哪里
Can't go anymore.

1401
01:05:55,160 --> 01:05:58,687
都会被抢、被杀或是被刺
Without getting mugged, or murdered, or stabbed.

1402
01:05:58,864 --> 01:06:01,128
小孩子枪杀同学
Kids killing their classmates, drive-by...

1403
01:06:01,300 --> 01:06:03,666
我甚至不敢再去邮局了
I won't even go into a post office anymore.

1404
01:06:03,802 --> 01:06:05,099
闭嘴，米区
- Shut up, Mitch! - You shut up!

1405
01:06:05,237 --> 01:06:06,204
你才闭嘴
I hate the bastard, but he's right.

1406
01:06:06,505 --> 01:06:08,200
我恨那个混蛋，但他说的对

1407
01:06:08,607 --> 01:06:09,699
知道要弄到枪有多容易吗？
You know how easy it is to get a gun?

1408
01:06:09,842 --> 01:06:11,776
五分钟，在枪展上
Five minutes, gun show...

1409
01:06:12,311 --> 01:06:14,142
我明白你孩子病了
I understand that your kid is sick, John.

1410
01:06:14,279 --> 01:06:16,804
但这算什么，我也有人生啊
But what makes him better than me?

1411
01:06:17,049 --> 01:06:18,380
对，但你有保险
I get a life too.

1412
01:06:18,517 --> 01:06:22,009
所以你要开枪？你跟警察说的
Yeah, but you got insurance.

1413
01:06:18,684 --> 01:06:20,276
So you're going to shoot me?

1414
01:06:20,419 --> 01:06:22,114
That's what you're telling the cops.

1415
01:06:22,154 --> 01:06:24,645
要是你儿子没得到心脏
If your son doesn't the very first heart available.

1416
01:06:24,790 --> 01:06:25,916
我们就死定了
We all die.

1417
01:06:27,793 --> 01:06:29,784
结局会怎样？
How's it going to end, John?

1418
01:06:30,028 --> 01:06:31,256
你打算怎么办？
What's your move?

1419
01:06:32,164 --> 01:06:35,395
我不打算怎样，我不知道
I got no move, okay?

1420
01:06:34,399 --> 01:06:35,491
I don't know what I'm going to do.

1421
01:06:38,737 --> 01:06:41,035
我在等待奇迹，好吗？
I'm waiting on a miracle, okay?

1422
01:06:42,241 --> 01:06:44,471
我在等待上帝的旨意
I'm waiting on an act of God.

1423
01:07:09,868 --> 01:07:11,597
亚契太太？
Mrs. Archibald?

1424
01:07:12,504 --> 01:07:14,563
我们可以谈谈吗？
Could we have a word with you, please?

1425
01:07:17,609 --> 01:07:19,099
这都是我的错
This is all my fault.

1426
01:07:19,244 --> 01:07:21,474
医院告诉我要麦克出院时
When the hospital told me they were releasing Mikey...

1427
01:07:21,613 --> 01:07:23,581
我打给约翰，对他乱吼
...I called John and I yelled at him.

1428
01:07:23,649 --> 01:07:25,879
还叫他要采取行动
And told him to do something, anything.

1429
01:07:26,018 --> 01:07:28,612
但我没想到K
But, I never thought...

1430
01:07:28,754 --> 01:07:29,880
我明白
I understand.

1431
01:07:30,022 --> 01:07:32,252
他有暴力倾向吗？
Is he a violent man, Mrs. Archibald?

1432
01:07:32,491 --> 01:07:37,292
没有，他温柔又亲切
No, no, he's sweet and gentle.

1433
01:07:37,796 --> 01:07:39,024
他连小虫都不敢打
He wouldn't hurt a fly.

1434
01:07:39,198 --> 01:07:42,133
他可不这么说，他说要杀人
That's not what he's saying.

1435
01:07:40,499 --> 01:07:42,194
He's talking about killing people.

1436
01:07:42,401 --> 01:07:44,801
我想知道的是K我可能多心了
Now, what I want to know is - I may be fishing here...

1437
01:07:44,937 --> 01:07:49,169
他是否在部队待过或什么的？
...but has he spent any time in the military or anything like that?

1438
01:07:51,276 --> 01:07:52,106
这是在干嘛？
- What is this? - What?

1439
01:07:52,244 --> 01:07:53,268
什么？

1440
01:07:54,346 --> 01:07:56,246
我知道了
I see what's going on here.

1441
01:07:58,050 --> 01:08:00,245
你想从我口中套话
You want me to say something.

1442
01:08:00,385 --> 01:08:01,977
好让你拿来对付我丈夫
That you can use against my husband.

1443
01:08:02,120 --> 01:08:03,417
他的麻烦大了
He's in a lot of trouble.

1444
01:08:03,488 --> 01:08:05,547
我们需要你去跟他谈谈
And we're going to need you to talk to him.

1445
01:08:05,624 --> 01:08:07,785
我们把话说明白点吧
Let's get something straight, mister.

1446
01:08:08,193 --> 01:08:11,651
你不能利用我去对付我丈夫
You cannot use me to build a case against my husband.

1447
01:08:11,830 --> 01:08:14,230
我支持他所做的每一件事
I support him in everything that he does.

1448
01:08:14,366 --> 01:08:16,425
我站在他那边，不是你这边
I'm on his side, not yours.

1449
01:08:16,602 --> 01:08:17,193
亚契太太
- Mrs. Archibald. - And you don't talk to me!

1450
01:08:17,369 --> 01:08:19,098
你别跟我说话

1451
01:08:21,340 --> 01:08:24,901
我可以说出我对你的看法
I would tell you what I think of you...

1452
01:08:26,011 --> 01:08:28,206
但我是虔诚的教徒
...but I'm a Christian woman.

1453
01:08:30,182 --> 01:08:31,444
请你们俩个离开
Now, you two leave me alone. I have a sick child to look after.

1454
01:08:31,617 --> 01:08:33,642
我还要照顾我生病的孩子

1455
01:08:38,223 --> 01:08:41,249
我已决定把麦克列入名单
I've decided to put Michael on the recipient list.

1456
01:08:43,028 --> 01:08:45,462
医院会负担所有费用
The hospital will pay for everything.

1457
01:08:47,432 --> 01:08:49,059
真的？
Really?

1458
01:08:49,334 --> 01:08:50,596
真的
Really.

1459
01:08:52,104 --> 01:08:53,594
谢谢你
Thank you.

1460
01:08:55,040 --> 01:08:57,372
天啊，谢谢你
Oh, God, thank you!

1461
01:09:04,650 --> 01:09:05,844
你真行
You're good.

1462
01:09:05,984 --> 01:09:08,145
什么？

1463
01:09:08,387 --> 01:09:09,718
表演的真棒
- Excuse me? - Quite the performance.

1464
01:09:10,022 --> 01:09:12,547
温暖的拥抱，诚挚的表情
The comforting embrace, the sincere look.

1465
01:09:12,658 --> 01:09:15,525
那一刹那，我真的相信你了
For a minute, I actually believed that you cared.

1466
01:09:28,440 --> 01:09:30,567
记者塔克在希望纪念医院
We go now to Hope Memorial Hospital live.

1467
01:09:30,676 --> 01:09:32,234
为您现场报导
Tuck Lampley.

1468
01:09:32,511 --> 01:09:35,378
在医院前的群众越聚越多
The crowd in front of Hope Memorial is growing.

1469
01:09:35,514 --> 01:09:38,005
特勤小组已经到达现场
The SWAT team has arrived.

1470
01:09:38,150 --> 01:09:39,208
现场情况变得相当紧张
And the situation is becoming very tense.

1471
01:09:39,351 --> 01:09:41,216
站在我身旁的是帕吉米
Standing next to me is James Palumbo.

1472
01:09:41,353 --> 01:09:42,786
约翰亚契的朋友
Friend of John Archibald.

1473
01:09:43,221 --> 01:09:45,917
帕先生，谈谈亚契先生吧
Mr. Palumbo, what can you tell us about John Archibald?

1474
01:09:46,825 --> 01:09:48,122
你知道K
You know...

1475
01:09:49,361 --> 01:09:52,125
我必须诚实，塔克
...I got to be honest, Tuck.

1476
01:09:52,698 --> 01:09:55,929
这整件事真是可怕
*This whole thing sucks, you know?

1477
01:09:56,835 --> 01:10:00,293
其实这都是可以避免的
*lt all could've been avoided so incredibly easy.

1478
01:10:00,973 --> 01:10:04,409
要是约翰是富翁就不会这样
None of this had to happen if John had been a millionaire.

1479
01:10:04,543 --> 01:10:08,035
他是石油大亨就好 但他不了解
Or, if his name was Rockefeller, but sometimes John don't get it.

1480
01:10:08,180 --> 01:10:12,116
这国家尊重的不是价值
He don't understand that.

1481
01:10:09,447 --> 01:10:12,348
What we hold sacred in this country isn't values.

1482
01:10:12,250 --> 01:10:14,377
重要的是价钱
It's value that's important.

1483
01:10:14,519 --> 01:10:16,510
我们有富人也有穷人
We got haves, we got have-nots.

1484
01:10:16,655 --> 01:10:19,749
有白领、蓝领阶级，有失业的
We got white-collar, blue-collar, and then we got no-collar.

1485
01:10:20,025 --> 01:10:21,458
所以医院
Inside there.

1486
01:10:21,593 --> 01:10:24,562
有豪华手术也有阳春手术
We got surgery, we got outpatient surgery...

1487
01:10:24,696 --> 01:10:27,290
还有烂手术
...and we got out-of-luck surgery.

1488
01:10:27,466 --> 01:10:28,865
这社会有很多人
There's a lot of people out there, Tuck.

1489
01:10:29,001 --> 01:10:31,595
很多根本没有25万的人
A lot of people here who don't got 250 grand.

1490
01:10:32,004 --> 01:10:35,462
把这样的人逼到绝境真是可耻
To shame a man like that and back him into a corner...

1491
01:10:35,941 --> 01:10:37,238
在我看来
...seems to me.

1492
01:10:37,676 --> 01:10:39,871
这是社会制度失序
Something is out of whack not someone.

1493
01:10:40,012 --> 01:10:42,981
我懂什么？我只是个工人
What do I know? I'm a factory worker.

1494
01:10:43,648 --> 01:10:45,445
看得出来这事令你很难过
I can see this is making you very upset...

1495
01:10:45,584 --> 01:10:47,814
但你若能面对镜头对约翰说话
...but, if you could speak to John Q. Right now.

1496
01:10:47,953 --> 01:10:49,181
你要说什么？
What would you say?

1497
01:10:49,321 --> 01:10:50,879
“帕吉米，约翰的友人”

1498
01:10:51,390 --> 01:10:53,620
我与你同在，你要保重
I'm there with you, and you take care.

1499
01:10:54,393 --> 01:10:56,361
这是一个朋友的心声
That's one man's opinion.

1500
01:10:56,495 --> 01:10:59,828
这是记者塔克的报导
Live at the crisis at Hope Memorial, this is Tuck Lampley.

1501
01:11:31,129 --> 01:11:32,357
怎么回事？
What's going on?

1502
01:11:32,531 --> 01:11:33,088
副队长
Were is everybody?

1503
01:11:33,265 --> 01:11:33,924
人呢？
We're sending a guy in through the air duct.

1504
01:11:34,099 --> 01:11:36,431
我们要派人从通风管进去

1505
01:11:37,402 --> 01:11:39,893
要是能让目标到这电话旁
If we can get the target to this phone, we got a clear shot.

1506
01:11:40,072 --> 01:11:41,039
我们就能动手射杀他
- Is that right? - Yes, lieutenant, that is right.

1507
01:11:41,206 --> 01:11:42,002
是吗？

1508
01:11:42,140 --> 01:11:44,404
是的，副队长，没错

1509
01:11:44,876 --> 01:11:45,934
When you're ready, chief.

1510
01:11:51,716 --> 01:11:54,241
就等你下令了，局长
Don't be nervous, guys.

1511
01:11:54,386 --> 01:11:56,547
别紧张，各位

1512
01:11:58,356 --> 01:11:59,823
老孟
Monroe!

1513
01:12:01,726 --> 01:12:02,954
我老婆要开骂了
My wife's calling.

1514
01:12:03,095 --> 01:12:04,756
更糟，是老爸要训话了
Worse, chief, it's Father Time.

1515
01:12:05,197 --> 01:12:06,664
你给我过来
Come over here!

1516
01:12:07,466 --> 01:12:10,094
别说了，法兰，我不想听
Not one word, Frank.

1517
01:12:10,268 --> 01:12:12,293
你这混蛋，在我背后搞小动作
Not one word, I don't want to hear- -

1518
01:12:10,368 --> 01:12:11,232
You son of bitch!

1519
01:12:12,471 --> 01:12:14,701
你要我怎么办？你看看时间
You're going behind my back!

1520
01:12:12,671 --> 01:12:14,070
What do you want from me, Frank?

1521
01:12:14,840 --> 01:12:16,068
看看你的表
Look at the clock! Look at your watch!

1522
01:12:16,208 --> 01:12:19,234
那家伙说一刻钟后就要开杀戒
The guy said at a quarter after, he's going o start killing peple- -

1523
01:12:19,377 --> 01:12:21,106
这太愚蠢了
- This is so goddamn stupid! - Then, what's your great idea?!

1524
01:12:21,246 --> 01:12:22,645
是吗？那你有什么好主意？

1525
01:12:22,781 --> 01:12:26,182
没什么好主意，特别是这个
There are no great ideas, especially this!

1526
01:12:26,318 --> 01:12:29,515
我有机会逮这家伙，我要动手
I got a shot at this guy, and I'm going to take it!

1527
01:12:29,654 --> 01:12:32,122
你做事老是不明快，你在说什么
You always take the open shot!

1528
01:12:32,257 --> 01:12:35,249
他老婆同意要跟他谈，让她来
What are you talking about?!

1529
01:12:32,524 --> 01:12:33,821
The wife has agreed to speak to him!

1530
01:12:33,892 --> 01:12:35,484
Let her talk him down.

1531
01:12:35,393 --> 01:12:37,088
我正打算这么做
That's exactly what I'm going to do.

1532
01:12:37,796 --> 01:12:39,229
利用他老婆逮他？
- Use the man's wife to set him up? - I'll use whatever work, Frnak.

1533
01:12:39,397 --> 01:12:42,696
什么有用我就用什么

1534
01:12:41,299 --> 01:12:42,197
Let me paint a picture for you.

1535
01:12:42,834 --> 01:12:44,199
我帮你描绘一下吧
Ok, what we have here is a lose/lose.

1536
01:12:44,336 --> 01:12:46,304
这是一个双输的局面
If he starts whacking hostages, it's bad!

1537
01:12:46,471 --> 01:12:48,234
要是他开始杀人质，就糟了
And if we give in to this asshole it's also bad!

1538
01:12:48,373 --> 01:12:49,863
但我们若向他投降，也很糟

1539
01:12:50,008 --> 01:12:50,804
对谁很糟？
Bad for who?

1540
01:12:50,942 --> 01:12:54,469
对大家都很糟，你、我、大家
It's bad for everybody! Me, you, everybody!

1541
01:12:54,679 --> 01:12:56,271
今年是选举年，就是很糟
It's an election year, it's just bad!

1542
01:12:56,414 --> 01:12:58,439
不管怎样，这家伙不能成功
However it goes down, Frank, this guy's not going to make it!

1543
01:12:58,583 --> 01:13:00,710
你要杀他？为选举铺路？
So you kill him?

1544
01:13:00,852 --> 01:13:02,717
死一个坏蛋没什么
That's a P.R. Bonanza, right?!

1545
01:13:00,985 --> 01:13:02,213
I can live with one dead bad guy!

1546
01:13:02,854 --> 01:13:04,378
我忍受不了的是
What I can't live with.

1547
01:13:04,523 --> 01:13:06,013
有无辜的市民受伤
Is one innocent person being hurt!

1548
01:13:06,158 --> 01:13:07,887
不能在我任内
Not one! Not on my watch!

1549
01:13:09,661 --> 01:13:11,424
法兰，你出局了
You know what, Frank? You're out!

1550
01:13:11,596 --> 01:13:12,585
我出局了？
I'm out?!

1551
01:13:12,697 --> 01:13:15,359
与个人无关，但你被停职了
No hard feelings, but you're relieved of duty.

1552
01:13:15,534 --> 01:13:16,762
从现在起由我主导
I'll handle this now.

1553
01:13:16,935 --> 01:13:17,765
你？
- You? - Yeah, me.

1554
01:13:17,903 --> 01:13:18,870
对，我
Think it's my first time in the dance floor?

1555
01:13:19,004 --> 01:13:20,665
你以为我这是第一次指挥？

1556
01:13:20,805 --> 01:13:22,796
你以为我是怎么得到这些的？
How do you think I got these?

1557
01:13:22,941 --> 01:13:24,306
小心点，别惹我
And watch it! Just watch it!

1558
01:13:24,442 --> 01:13:27,468
我承受很多压力，很多人在看
I got a lot of pressure on me, Frank. A lot of eye's watching.

1559
01:13:27,646 --> 01:13:30,638
总要有人行动，而你不行动
Someone's got to make the call.

1560
01:13:29,047 --> 01:13:30,810
You're not going to do it!

1561
01:13:30,782 --> 01:13:32,044
那就由我来
I'll do it.

1562
01:13:32,951 --> 01:13:35,419
那些人质怎么办？
What about the hostages, the human beings?!

1563
01:13:35,554 --> 01:13:37,351
他们最好小心点
Better keep their heads down.

1564
01:13:49,801 --> 01:13:50,631
太好了
Great.

1565
01:13:50,769 --> 01:13:51,394
怎么回事？
- What is it? - The air-conditioning just turned off.

1566
01:13:51,570 --> 01:13:53,697
